column4: Package compiz-core has no available version, but exists in the database.
I had it installed before on another system
when i try to install compiz-core i get this error: Package compiz-core has no available version, but exists in the database.
when i try to install compiz-core i get this error: Package compiz-core has no available version, but exists in the database.
try this.  sudo aptitude update; sudo aptitude install compiz-core
i think that did the trick
